This is an endless rogue-like where you and up to three other players team up to face endless waves of enemies, growing stronger as you go. 🔥

WITH OVER 50 unique classes,
117 upgrades,
22 companions, 
and 115 weapons 
...I think you can imagine how many endless builds you’ll be able to create! 🧪

❤️ The game was highly inspired by previous rogue-like titles such as Brotato, Risk of Rain 2, and Gunfire Reborn, but also by some Roblox games such as Randomly Generated Droids and RogueBlade. So if you know and enjoyed those, I’m sure you’ll get the hang of our game pretty quickly.

⚠️ Disclaimer : Since it's a BETA, some classes may not have their extra outfits available right away... but don’t worry, that’s coming soon. Also with so many possible builds and outcomes, the game might be a bit unbalanced at first... but we’ll do our best to release patches as often as possible.

This game is a true test of your survival and PvP skills. Prepare to face challenges that will test your abilities to the fullest.

Please be aware that this game is still in development and does not represent the final product. Expect frequent updates and occasional restarts. While your skins and delta currency will be retained, player inventories and non-permanent items may be reset with significant updates.

We are inspired by the original Deadzone on Roblox and express our sincere appreciation to its creator for the incredible game idea that ignited our own creative journey.
